<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes" ?>
<panel
 height="380"
 layout="topleft"
 name="panel_outfit_snapshot_inventory"
 width="490">
    <icon
     follows="top|left"
     height="18"
     image_name="Snapshot_Inventory"
     layout="topleft"
     left="12"
     mouse_opaque="true"
     name="title_icon"
     top="6"
     width="18" />
    <text
     follows="top|left|right"
     font="SansSerifBold"
     height="14"
     layout="topleft"
     left_pad="12"
     length="1"
     name="title"
     right="-10"
     text_color="white"
     type="string"
     top_delta="3">
        인벤토리
    </text>
    <view_border 
     bevel_style="in"
     follows="left|top|right" 
     height="1"
     left="9"
     layout="topleft"
     name="hr"
     right="-5"
     top_pad="5"
     />
    <text
     follows="top|left"
     font="SansSerif"
     height="126"
     layout="topleft"
     left="10"
     length="1"
     name="hint_lbl"
     top_pad="6"
     width="200"
     type="string"
     word_wrap="true">
이미지를 인벤토리에 업로드하려면 L$[UPLOAD_COST]가 필요합니다.

요금은 가입 수준에 따라 결정됩니다. 수준이 높을수록 낮은 수수료가 부과됩니다.
    </text>
    <button
     follows="right|bottom"
     height="23"
     label="취소"
     layout="topleft"
     name="cancel_btn"
     right="-5"
     top="337"
     width="97">
      <button.commit_callback
       function="Inventory.SaveOutfitCancel" />
    </button>
    <button
     follows="left|bottom"
     height="23"
     label="저장"
     layout="topleft"
     left="10"
     name="save_btn"
     top_delta="0"
     width="97">
      <button.commit_callback
       function="Inventory.SaveOutfitPhoto" />
    </button>
</panel>
